  "text": "where λ 1 = 100 and λ 2 = 250 in our experiments. Content loss We adopt the traditional content loss to direct the output of generator to ground truth. Although both L 1 and L 2 norm are commonly used, L 1 norm is chosen since it attains less blurring result [CITATION_1] .",
